>Can this be used as an overnight charger??  I mean, 2 amps is pretty 
>significant, and I measured the output at 15.5 volts DC, more than the 
>rated 12 volts.
>
>This beast weighs 1.5 kg so it is not economical to mail.   Anyone local 
>who would like me to pick one up and hold it, the store closes Saturday, 
